A profile is a tiddler whose:

* ''title'' — anything human-readable
* ''type'' — `application/json`
* ''tags'' — include `$:/tags/json-convert/profile`
* ''text'' — JSON conforming to the schema below

```
{
  "records":       "{{...}}",            ← required, path to the records array
  "tw-fields":     { ... bindings ... }, ← required, must include "title"
  "custom-fields": { ... bindings ... }  ← optional
}
```

